      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RONZEL SONNY (2) draws much better than he did last start at Bathurst when he came from the back row. Led from one spot wider than this when he won at Junee two runs ago so has the speed to take advantage of this barrier. FESTINALENTE (10) may need some luck from this barrier but is proven at this circuit and distance and is going well having scored at Bathurst three runs ago before another good effort last time out when third at that same venue. RIVERINA FLASH (1) drew wide and broke but still managed to finish third at Bathurst last time out. With manners he should get his chance from the inside barrier. GLENN FORD NZ (3) draws well and showed pleasing improvement last time out when third from the back line at Dubbo.",
